S|# YVON Dashboard — Rules & Never-Again Patterns|> LONG-TERM. YVON dashboard-specific only. System-wide rules → docs/mem/feedback.md // > Schema: each rule must have [added: YYYY-MM-DD] · Rules without dates are invalid. // > 🔴 CRITICAL · 🟡 IMPORTANT · 🟢 GUIDANCE // ---
S|🔴 CRITICAL|- [added: 2026-03-01] Never hardcode colors — always use CSS variable tokens from globals.css // - [added: 2026-03-01] SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY is server-only — never expose to browser or client components // - [added: 2026-03-01] No localStorage for persistent data — Supabase only; localStorage for ephemeral UI state only // - [added: 2026-04-19] CEO dashboard background: light blue `public/Background Image.jpg` — NO dark overlay on top, ever. It kills the light palette. // - [added: 2026-04-1
S|🟡 IMPORTANT|- [added: 2026-04-19] Font sizing: never below 12px for readable text. 800 weight throughout the dashboard. // - [added: 2026-04-19] Each list item gets its own glass card — no shared containers for list rows // - [added: 2026-04-19] Any list that can grow needs maxHeight + overflowY: auto. Default: 360–420px max. // - [added: 2026-05-10] NavBar: .glass-nav class, always dark navy (#0c2c52) text — never text-white inside the nav // - [added: 2026-05-10] War Room: RoutingChain component must alwa
S|🟢 GUIDANCE|- [added: 2026-04-19] KPI metrics: individual V1 cards with 220×64 sparklines, not a combined strip // - [added: 2026-04-19] Dark pill elements (Ticker, TabStrip): background rgba(8,16,36,0.58) // - [added: 2026-03-01] Mark components 'use client' only when using hooks, browser APIs, or event handlers // - [added: 2026-03-01] No unnecessary useEffect — prefer RSC data fetching or useSWR // ---
S|Never Again|- [added: 2026-04-19] CEO dashboard — applied dark overlay on light background image → killed the glass aesthetic entirely. Rule: never add any rgba overlay on top of the background image.